{"tid":874780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超浪漫Kiss！日排美男hehe情深","createTime":"2018-10-24T12:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T14:04:46.000Z","uid":3189,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"827f4e5241a22a2b7a7091764e0a56c1f5f7d087","tid":874780,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203105_cb3229b0b29bc3eebb6a8cae75b728f9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203105_cb3229b0b29bc3eebb6a8cae75b728f9.gif&h=15ee4efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203108_badc31cdc185853cf5ee77254e59db87.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203108_badc31cdc185853cf5ee77254e59db87.gif&h=f2886fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n能成為密友總帶着愛，咁敵人又點先？一樣都可以好有愛，仲鍾意到男男咀嘴添！日前男排V League男子全明星賽，山本湧同高松卓矢各為其主，雙方因一次挑釁，大家嘈起上嚟，高松卓矢勁躁走過網推撞山本湧，全場觀眾以為會打交嘅時候，佢兩個竟然直接咀對咀錫咗一啖，令全場女FansV嘩鬼叫，大家都高叫「好有愛」，唔單只將場波氣氛推到高峰，全場觀眾更加高潮叠起！ <br />\n<br />\nV League喺日本好受歡迎，唔少球手勁靚仔，又夠高大威猛喎，好多少女都畀佢哋迷到癲。呢次全明星賽，大牌明星全部喺晒度，本身已經好有睇頭，但喺第一局，山本湧同高松卓矢就做場好戲畀大家睇。當時山本湧見對友得分，竟然伸手挑釁高松卓矢，高松見到好唔老利，開始出口鬧對手，之後仲走過網推山本湧心口添。當以為唔知點收科時，佢兩個竟然咀嘴，山本湧之後仲好回味咁用手抹抹個嘴添，成場即刻勁尖叫，令到啲女Fans超開心囉。 <br />\n<br />\n其實好多明星賽，都有啲特別嘢睇，呢次高松卓矢走過網找山本湧晦氣時，啲隊友個個笑晒口，完全冇阻止意圖，就明顯係知佢兩個只係玩嘢。但現場觀眾同所有Fans，都絕對唔介意佢哋做戲，因為呢齣戲真係好睇囉。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203135_e6e849c6d8ab90eaccfca259dfa5138c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203135_e6e849c6d8ab90eaccfca259dfa5138c.png&h=39778d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山本湧(左)同高松卓矢嚟個深情一吻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203139_21673e0426c78402f223a6acdadb0a18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203139_21673e0426c78402f223a6acdadb0a18.png&h=624c0f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203141_fecfa53183d6b079528e750ffe0524ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203141_fecfa53183d6b079528e750ffe0524ed.png&h=779e10b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203143_a32199145c717f24715f6a421eec20c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203143_a32199145c717f24715f6a421eec20c3.png&h=bb2b7d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山本湧(左)好cutie。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/203146_38eeae3f02dcd5c038c91fb1ea8c7b30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F203146_38eeae3f02dcd5c038c91fb1ea8c7b30.png&h=4dc5dd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山本湧係個暖男喔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170328/mobile/bkn-20170328160044447-0328_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170328%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170328160044447-0328_00882_001.html&d=TfZYDYXcrxxb4%2B8FkDEgtttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f6d95055\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170328/mobile/bkn-20170328160044447-0328_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"767cc78437ae655c7a9d64f1d8266ec3e732859a","tid":874780,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54354b5c509a4536d3b3298dbd6054f0858f901","tid":874780,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"Please respect gays"},{"pid":"eab645eea2990f8f62ec4cb49c68d51d8b6b5917","tid":874780,"uid":24160,"li